  <h1>What is functional programming?</h1>
  <div class="artmeta"><span>By Coldwast</span><span>Updated Jun 15, 2026</span><span>7 min read</span><span class="tag">#functional</span><span class="tag">#paradigms</span><span class="tag">#concepts</span></div>
  <nav class="toc" id="toc"></nav>
  <figure>
    <img class="hero" src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517180102446-f3ece451e9d8?w=1200&q=80&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Lines of source code on a dark screen" width="1200" height="420" loading="eager" />
